                    <name>richTextValue</name>
                    <value>&lt;p&gt;Hey {{{Recipient.FirstName}}},&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;First off, we wanted to say congratulations on taking a huge step in your personalized precision wellness journey! You&amp;rsquo;re already ahead of most by investing in yourself to truly understand how your body functions.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

